00:16:06.583 --> 00:16:08.660
But they're still here.

00:16:08.793 --> 00:16:10.665
Inside.

00:16:12.338 --> 00:16:14.460
And here.

00:16:15.091 --> 00:16:16.592
With you.

00:16:16.593 --> 00:16:20.467
