00:17:08.278 --> 00:17:11.458
One more.
And last one.

00:17:11.483 --> 00:17:13.526
There you go.

00:17:13.694 --> 00:17:14.773
I'll see you guys.

00:17:14.798 --> 00:17:15.978
Oh.

00:17:25.027 --> 00:17:26.445
Watch where you're going.

00:17:26.446 --> 00:17:28.147
