What's happening?

00:24:13.400 --> 00:24:15.527
En Sabah Nur.
En Sabah Nur.

00:24:25.574 --> 00:24:27.608
Something's wrong.
No. No.

00:24:27.633 --> 00:24:30.625
- Run!
- Quick, run!

00:25:04.536 --> 00:25:06.949
