or the telekinesis...

00:27:35.706 --> 00:27:37.908
it's something else.

00:27:38.770 --> 00:27:43.533
Some dark power inside
and it's growing.

00:27:43.558 --> 00:27:45.741
Like a fire.

00:27:45.891 --> 00:27:47.526
